{
  "stem": "13382.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because see, I mean, she was sort of a-- she was the same, except different name, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so that was these two Yugoslav, and was a very excellent designer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these two Yugoslav were illegally in Budapest as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They was connected with the partisan-- Yugoslavian partisan connection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think one of them, who was a typical German looking-- and he spoke German-- I think he was at [GERMAN], out of-- and a communist.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I think he killed an SS officer there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he and his accomplice-- the other one-- they had to leave that area, and they came to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because again, sort of they could-- and this-- so it just, by coincidence, and that was Edith there, and that was another blonde, blue-eyed Jewish girl from Romania.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So there was no doubt about these people, right, that they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody was accepted that they are what they are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on the end, they took over this salon, because it was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, they took the [NON-ENGLISH] away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so they-- they carried on with the business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Edith reasonably safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, myself, that time I still moved in with my-- with mother and Frank, into that house in Verseny utca--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in one room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was designated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't locked up yet, but obviously their ultimate plan was to create a ghetto there, which it became, on the end, in any case.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] we were-- we had where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could buy things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were restricted of moving because I think you had to have a yellow star and there-- there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can go only this time of the day out, and that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And always-- something always happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
